"<1.so>Well, well...if it isn't the all-knowing\n"
"young man."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_002"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I'm in the market for a little something to\n"
"pique my curiosity, so I spend my time\n"
"gazing into the horizon."
msgstr ""

