msgctxt "Talk_003"
msgid ""
"<1.so>When did I get so old?<2.pa><3.ra><4.so>If I still had my youth, "
"I'd be off in a\n"
"flash, in search of something...\n"
"fascinating.\n"
"But this prison of old bones has\n"
"condemned me to a short future of\n"
"staring off into the unknown.<5.pa>"
msgstr ""

